# IT References
### Common Ports:
- 20/21 FTP, 22 SSH, 23 Telnet, 25 SMTP, 53 DNS, 80 HTTP, 110 POP3, 143 IMAP, 443 HTTPS, 3389 RDP
### Windows Commands:
- ipconfig, ping, netstat, sfc, chkdsk, tasklist, shutdown /r
### Linux Commands:
- ls, cd, pwd, grep, sudo, cat, df, top
### Troubleshooting Steps:
- Identify → Hypothesize → Test → Verify → Document
### Networking Devices:
- Router — connects networks
- Switch — connects devices
- Access Point — wireless network hub
- Modem — translates ISP signal
- Firewall — monitors and blocks unsafe traffic
